longBusinessSummary: MAHLE Metal Leve S.A., an automotive parts company, manufactures and sells components for internal combustion engines and automotive filters in South America, Europe, Central and North America, Africa, Asia, Oceania, and the Middle East. The company offers air conditioning systems, air management systems, cylinder and engine cooling components, electronics, mechatronics, piston systems, valve train systems, and, oil and fuel management systems for passenger cars and commercial vehicles. It provides climatic wind tunnels, engine testing, engineering, module testing, thermal management, and transmission services. MAHLE Metal Leve S.A. was founded in 1920 and is headquartered in Mogi Guaçu, Brazil.
